{"tid":1412683,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！！！青x酒店&華x酒店高層恐嚇員工8月5射波即炒！後果自負！","createTime":"2019-08-05T07:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T03:47:59.000Z","uid":120411,"like":135,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9e98bccc886d81cdf63d34c33a5dd4b7b14606","tid":1412683,"uid":120411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:32:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">代po！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由於事太嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n青衣2間酒店高層<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">「曾鑑波」</span></span>發言表示：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">8月5日如有員工射波或罷工 後果自負，嚴重會即炒！！！</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">前枱經理李振文和大部分GSM亦是深藍！</span></span>不允許前枱職員今日射波，以強力言語去恐嚇他們！如有下屬企圖罷工或射波 交名上報 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即炒！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9mq7561.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9mq7561.png&h=40548dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sDkWZr1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsDkWZr1.png&h=f2587ff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">不但今日8月5日全港罷工，仲有6月12日三罷！高層都極力阻止員工罷工！當日罷工的職員事後被照見高層！可見2間酒店既深藍甚多，而且佢地成日會係酒店拎啲示威者出黎討論甚至發表深藍意見，想令其他原本係黃絲既人都變哂同佢地一樣係深藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我懇請在座咁多位想爆房嘅巴打和絲打慎重考慮，如需要爆房請選擇黃絲酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你地識揀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"88e342d009ff7b197598592e7cc5a0ce0cb94448","tid":1412683,"uid":104399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:34:35.000Z","msg":"哇屌....."},{"pid":"18acd95d47ac6dc386c8d4d14a03295dcb9f23a4","tid":1412683,"uid":104399,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:35:58.000Z","msg":"間酒店好多大陸閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664637d5cbfe98edad920224cf06abf482e3acd6","tid":1412683,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:36:14.000Z","msg":"點樣可以幫呢間野宣傳<br />\n有冇啲book酒店網可以比comment"},{"pid":"4ce3ed603d429e33f59677a1a718d2fd20ebb035","tid":1412683,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3bfb566a8164d94741ae6ac4fdecafc9a0621c","tid":1412683,"uid":49128,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:37:15.000Z","msg":"直接開全名啦，使鬼xx咩"},{"pid":"079cdfeb256f659af0846454eb6861c6e282df86","tid":1412683,"uid":92021,"like":0,"