 />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">不但今日8月5日全港罷工，仲有6月12日三罷！高層都極力阻止員工罷工！當日罷工的職員事後被照見高層！可見2間酒店既深藍甚多，而且佢地成日會係酒店拎啲示威者出黎討論甚至發表深藍意見，想令其他原本係黃絲既人都變哂同佢地一樣係深藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我懇請在座咁多位想爆房嘅巴打和絲打慎重考慮，如需要爆房請選擇黃絲酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你地識揀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:29:00.000Z","msg":"開埋其他GSM名啦, 等其他酒店唔好請佢哋"},{"pid":"511b64c42381575575be44bf69bc626a67080015","tid":1412683,"uid":296422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32ad693a293834a2f17fae5e250a6c7a407d7f3","tid":1412683,"uid":157503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:01:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"d0d982f47674cd5d60524a80ee3038fe70094cb2","tid":1412683,"uid":105593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:11:33.000Z","msg":"有無人一齊去佢地Facebook 或者去trip advisor一齊數臭佢地 比其他旅客睇到"},{"pid":"7ffe39e9651a47c7df5c2f8295c502c7bb2c25d9","tid":1412683,"uid":47924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:53:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d1edfdca46e0787723d286200bea306bb8c5571","tid":1412683,"uid"